Mojolicious-Plugin-RedirectHost

Mojolicious Plugin. It redirects requests to the main host. Useful for SEO.

USAGE

Generate 301 redirect from C<http://mirror.main.host/path?query> to C<http://main.host/path?query>
  
  # Mojolicious
  $app->plugin('RedirectHost', host => 'main.host');
  
  # Mojolicious::Lite
  plugin RedirectHost => { host => 'main.host' };


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

